{"tid":1958453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台記者違反一中原則擴大追究，台灣外交部：恥辱！","createTime":"2020-04-04T16:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T08:35:34.000Z","uid":337052,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"32fc579756efd22b6393ac97de7c858f2be678fa","tid":1958453,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T16:06:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傳港記者違反一中原則擴大追究 吳釗燮：恥辱</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2020/04/04 19:11<br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者游凱翔台北4日電）世界衛生組織高級顧問艾沃德3月底接受港媒訪問，提及台灣時視訊疑斷訊，事後傳記者因違反「一個中國」擴大追究責任；外交部長吳釗燮今天表示，這真是恥辱，台灣人將與港人站在一起追求真相。<br />\n<br />\n2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫情在全球持續延燒，世界衛生組織（WHO）高級顧問艾沃德3月28日接受香港電台記者視訊訪問，被問到世衛是否重新考慮接納台灣時，他一度顯然裝作沒聽見，接著疑似切斷視訊。重新接通後，記者再提問台灣，艾沃德顧左右而言他，稱讚中國防疫做得很好。<br />\n<br />\n當時吳釗燮在Twitter上發文表示：「哇，在WHO連台灣兩個字都不能提啊？」並強調，在對抗全球大流行疫情的時刻，WHO應該把政治放一邊。<br />\n<br />\n有媒體報導，傳出香港特區政府有關單位認為，這名記者行為已違「一個中國」原則，要追究廣播處長兼香港電台總編輯梁家榮的責任。<br />\n<br />\n吳釗燮晚間再度於Twitter上發文表示，很遺憾看到以前被視為東亞媒體自由燈塔的香港，如今演變至此，這真是恥辱，台灣人民會與香港人民站在一起，追求真相。（編輯：張良知）1090404<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MOFA_Taiwan/status/1246336689334677506?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMOFA_Taiwan%2Fstatus%2F1246336689334677506%3Fs%3D20&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=5616d29a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMOFA_Taiwan%2Fstatus%2F1246336689334677506%3Fs%3D20&h=b35d11c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MOFA_Taiwan/status/1246336689334677506?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"33991e6c11622b33825c5abb5f6e83bb880afe07","tid":1958453,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T16:19:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">印度女主播大罵中共：誰理你「一中原則」<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GZEYkL4zc94\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGZEYkL4zc94&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=e311538b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GZEYkL4zc94</a>"},{"pid":"d78818b42cc2e67fca56a65328370cc39af81f01","tid":1958453,"uid":205462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:04:57.000Z","msg":"侵侵上台無耐嗰陣，都曾經不解點解美國要遵守&quot;一個蝗國&quot;嘅原則，之後就無再响呢個議題上發表意見了"},{"pid":"dad12c86802e5d372dce83a83ef07c0f4ecbf9fe","tid":1958453,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d78818b42cc2e67fca56a65328370cc39af81f01","tid":1958453,"uid":205462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:04:57.000Z","msg":"侵侵上台無耐嗰陣，都曾經不解點解美國要遵守&quot;一個蝗國&quot;嘅原則，之後就無再响呢個議題上發表意見了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:19:45.000Z","msg":"現在美國已經沒有「一中原則」<br />\n<br />\n向全球分享「台灣模式」！ 美國務院讚：台灣是防疫領導者<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3122529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3122529&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=fc8e1cb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3122529&h=d77209f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3122529</a>"},{"pid":"42cd8fd50c14631078e9bb0999659ff7fd91b2a8","tid":1958453,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T08:35:34.000Z","msg":"今日搞咩炒記者集會"}]}